{"tid":1078743,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"希望自己20歲時明白的十件事","createTime":"2019-03-26T12:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T16:10:05.000Z","uid":68430,"like":47,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c4bc78d17eb30e6b97ca5acbfb04c464d9e51272","tid":1078743,"uid":68430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T12:45:44.000Z","msg":"1 不要那麼介意別人的說話，不少是隨意說說<br />\n2 父母可能不是最對，但他們是最愛你的<br />\n3 在社會有很多像會幫助自己的人，其實是在利用你<br />\n4 父母幫到的可能很微小， 但他們總是樂意幫助你<br />\n5 工作的環境愈多晉升機會， 人事便愈複雜，鬥爭愈激烈<br />\n6 不要妄想幫人便被人接納，有時別人當你傻瓜<br />\n7 有時幫了人別人會記住， 在以後向你伸出援手<br />\n8 愈有實力， 便招來愈多妒忌<br />\n9 即使幫人， 也可能使人沒面子， 或招來旁人妒忌<br />\n10 在年輕時， 要勇敢點追夢， 大了可承受的風險便小了<br />\n- by 仁秀郊"},{"pid":"54bc68759efee47633bbaa7308a266a26557841b","tid":1078743,"uid":68430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:09:28.000Z","msg":"😄"},{"pid":"f0ed516296727248de76a85036da696121f0b36f","tid":1078743,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:12:05.000Z","msg":"中二病"},{"pid":"091578c96cafd919876664c24649b93ac849bf0b","tid":1078743,"uid":36383,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:12:42.000Z","msg":"我廿歲已經識咁樣： 🤚😑🤚"},{"pid":"cdc870675cd4074fcf7d2ce867415aa9943c8084","tid":1078743,"uid":3549,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:34:32.000Z","msg":"1.要戴condom<br />\n2.不要中出"},{"pid":"b541c74622e6c7475faaa69579a257d8a9e893fc","tid":1078743,"uid":68430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"091578c96cafd919876664c24649b93ac849bf0b","tid":1078743,"uid":36383,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:12:42.000Z","msg":"我廿歲已經識咁樣： 🤚😑🤚"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T13:40:35.000Z","msg":"叻仔😃"},{"pid":"34d71f497e5ab0c3276e5c12c16dd89c560faf7d","tid":1078743,"uid":68430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cdc870675cd4074fcf7d2ce867415aa9943c8084","tid":1078743,"uid":3549,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTim